{% extends 'base/base.html.twig' %}
{% block body %}
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <p>
                Our community thrives on curiosity, creativity, and collaboration. To ensure a safe and welcoming space for everyone, all members are expected to follow this Code of Conduct.
            </p>
            <h2>1. Respectful Interactions</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Treat all participants with respect, kindness, and patience.</li>
                <li>Value different perspectives and approaches to puzzles.</li>
                <li>Assume good intentions, and clarify misunderstandings before escalating.</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>2. No Abuse or Harassment</h2>
            <p>Harassment, hate speech, or discriminatory remarks (including based on race, gender, age, ability, religion, sexual orientation, or nationality) will not be tolerated.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Personal attacks, insults, or inflammatory language are prohibited.</li>
                <li>Do not share explicit, offensive, or otherwise inappropriate content.</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>3. Collaboration and Fair Play</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Share ideas and solutions constructively without spoiling the experience for others.</li>
                <li>Give credit when building on someone else’s contribution.</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>
                4. Privacy and Safety
            </h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Do not share personal information about yourself or others without consent.</li>
                <li>Respect the confidentiality of private messages and collaborations.</li>
                <li>Do not use the platform to promote scams, phishing, or malicious links.</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>5. Responsible Use of the Platform</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Use the site features as intended—avoid spam, flooding, or disruptive behavior.</li>
                <li>Report bugs responsibly; do not exploit them to gain unfair advantages.</li>
                <li>Follow moderator instructions promptly and respectfully.</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>6. Enforcement</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Violations of this Code may result in warnings, temporary suspensions, or permanent bans, at the discretion of the moderators.</li>
                <li>Repeated or severe misconduct may result in immediate removal from the community.</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>7. Community Spirit</h2>
            <p>This site is built for players of all levels. Let’s help each other learn, grow, and have fun together.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
